<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.college-cram.com/study/accounting/presentations/724" class="external text" title="http://www.college-cram.com/study/accounting/presentations/724" rel="nofollow">Professor Cram. "Accounting Cycle: General Ledger Accounting" College-Cram.com. 13 May 2008 &lt;http://www.college-cram.com/study/accounting/presentations/724&gt;</a></li>
</ol>


